From Jerry Cruce Subject Re Inner tube in tyre Safe Speedy Mercer wrote In article A writes Hello DoD'ers et al , I need some advice on inner tubes in tubeless tyres Barry Manor DoD Spend the bucks and get a new tire DoD Technician Dr Speed NOT Student I second the commend from Dr Speed, get a new tire It's like your brakes, something you don't want to take chances with I waited too long to take care of my front tire once and it went flat on me, doing MPH going down the grapevine towards Bakersfield At that instance, I would of given any amount of money for a new tire I'm lucky to be here Jerry